{"tid":1992670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★香港仔Walker Shop結業 未知是否全數分店結業。","createTime":"2020-04-28T09:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T07:19:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f91808e2b9f6c710e745dee612fb4457c98493c7","tid":1992670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"位於九龍窩打老道的一間夜冷店「大福行夜冷」在fb表示，香港仔Walker Shop結業，夜冷店將接收十板貨，「今天已落四板到大福行鋪頭開賣中，所有男，女款一律每對$40大平賣！」<br />\n<br />\n店家貼出圖中可見，當中有各式的時款鞋，包括波鞋、高跟鞋和短靴等等，不過店家回覆沒有帆船鞋或皮鞋。夜冷店負責人表示，有興趣就到店舖選擇，但不清楚是否全數Walker Shop分店都已結業。<br />\n<br />\nWalker Shop在去年開始多間分店已相繼結業，當時有傳媒報道只剩下香港仔及天水圍兩間分店仍營業。本網曾致電香港仔及天水圍的Walker Shop，電話均已取消，Walker Shop的facebook亦於2018年停止更新，公司網頁亦已上不到。早在2018年4月旺角Walker Shop的捲閘曾遭人淋潑白色油漆，並遺下追數單張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/466087/%E5%A4%9C%E5%86%B7%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6walker-shop%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%81-%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E9%9E%8B%E6%AC%BE40%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B3%E8%B3%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F466087%2F%25E5%25A4%259C%25E5%2586%25B7%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%2594%25B6walker-shop%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%2581-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%259E%258B%25E6%25AC%25BE40%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25B3%25A3&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=de465f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/466087/%E5%A4%9C%E5%86%B7%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6walker-shop%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%81-%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3%E9%9E%8B%E6%AC%BE40%E5%85%83%E5%B9%B3%E8%B3%A3</a>"},{"pid":"b44af61b54e0960b177a0e942e1f31642be6d71b","tid":1992670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331516029442330625.jpeg/DBtrjml06Z